<D>__{what about money?}
<C>__{chance}
<D>__{i never needed money.}
<A>__{franklin steps to the tv, turns it off.}
<C>__{franklin}
<D>__{mr. chance, perhaps you could show us some identification with your address a driver's license, a credit card, checkbook?}
<C>__{chance}
<D>__{no, i do not have any of those.}
<C>__{franklin}
<D>__{then how about medical records? could you give us the name of your doctor, or your dentist?}
